  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Your skin is an odd tint that somehow absorbs background colors. Maybe because your mother drank a lot of potions when you were still inside her belly. Maybe because you've been blessed by the barghests. Maybe because you're just better than the other boring goblins.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Goblin</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>You gain a +2 trait bonus on Stealth checks, providing you wear only light armor or no armor.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Pathfinder Society</strong></p>\n<p>Only legal goblin PCs are allowed to choose this trait.</p>",
